pea, pie and pud
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:the usual colloquial abbrev. form of the main fare at pie-carts: =pea, pie and spud (mashed potatoes)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:pie-cart
Pronunciation:
Notes: ca1945 at least. Wellington.
